column2: wol_chla_plot <- ggplot(wol_chla, aes(x=as.numeric(Year), y=as.numeric(result))) + stat_summary(fun.y = "mean", geom = "point") + ylab("Chlorophyll a (ug/L)") + xlab("Year") + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1)) + ggtitle("Chlorophyll a in West Okoboji Lake From 2002-2022") + geom_smooth(method=lm) + scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(2002, 2022, 1))
